      <Value><![CDATA[<p>NOTES TO EDITOR</p>
<ul>
<li>QMU has been supporting public service organisations at the University for ten years. Over that time we have supported over 100 students and many public and Third Sector employers to meet the ongoing challenges and uncertainties surrounding public service delivery. Our Master of Public Administration is the only MPA in Scotland. We provide the opportunity to gain insights from international examples of public administration and to critically discuss future developments with fellow learners, academics and experienced guest speakers. Modules include International Trends in Public Administration, Leading Change in Public Services and Workplace Learning. There are competitive rates available for public sector employers who sponsor students on the programme.</li>
</ul>
